msgstr "https://github.com/Lexo0522/Ding-Pusher"

#. Description of the plugin
#: ding-pusher.php
msgid "自动将 WordPress 新文章与新用户注册消息推送到钉钉机器人。"
msgstr "Automatically push WordPress new posts and new user registration messages to DingTalk bots."

