#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:499
msgid "在钉钉群中创建自定义机器人。"
msgstr "Create a custom bot in a DingTalk group."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:500
msgid "根据机器人安全设置选择关键词 / 加签 / IP 白名单。"
msgstr "Choose Keyword / Signature / IP Whitelist based on the bot's security settings."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:501
msgid "复制机器人 Webhook 地址，粘贴到设置页并保存。"
msgstr "Copy the bot Webhook URL, paste it into the settings page, and save."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:502
msgid "点击“发送测试消息”验证配置。"
msgstr "Click \"Send Test Message\" to verify the configuration."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:503
msgid "开启触发场景与模板，观察推送记录。"
msgstr "Enable triggers and templates, then check the push records."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:508
msgid "配置清单"
msgstr "Configuration Checklist"

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:510
msgid "Webhook：填入机器人 Webhook 地址，并确认可访问。"
msgstr "Webhook: Enter the bot Webhook URL and ensure it is reachable."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:511
msgid "安全校验：按机器人安全设置选择关键词 / 加签 / IP 白名单。"
msgstr "Security: Choose Keyword / Signature / IP Whitelist based on bot settings."

