msgid "触发场景：选择新文章、更新或新用户注册。"
msgstr "Triggers: Choose new posts, updates, or new user registrations."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:513
msgid "消息模板：按需调整文本、链接或 Markdown 模板。"
msgstr "Templates: Adjust text, link, or Markdown templates as needed."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:514
msgid "保存并发送测试消息验证配置。"
msgstr "Save and send a test message to verify."

