msgid "排查清单"
msgstr "Troubleshooting Checklist"

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:572
msgid "测试消息失败：检查 Webhook、安全设置与服务器网络。"
msgstr "Test message failed: check Webhook, security settings, and server network access."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:573
msgid "新文章未推送：确认已开启触发、文章状态为已发布，并检查 WP-Cron。"
msgstr "No new post push: ensure triggers are enabled, post is published, and WP-Cron is running."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:574
msgid "导出失败：检查上传目录权限或改用 CSV。"
msgstr "Export failed: check uploads permissions or use CSV."

