msgstr "Rate limit: exports are throttled; try again later."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:580
msgid "常见问题"
msgstr "FAQ"

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:582
msgid "如何配置关键词安全？"
msgstr "How do I configure keyword security?"

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:583
msgid "在钉钉机器人安全设置中添加关键词，同时在插件安全方式选择“关键词”并填入相同关键词。"
msgstr "Add a keyword in the bot’s security settings, then select “Keyword” and enter the same value in the plugin."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:586
msgid "如何使用加签？"
msgstr "How do I use signature mode?"

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:587
msgid "选择“加签”，填写机器人密钥，插件会自动生成签名。"
msgstr "Select “Signature”, enter the bot secret, and the plugin will generate the signature."

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:590
msgid "为什么没有推送记录？"
msgstr "Why are there no push records?"

#: admin/class-ding-pusher-admin.php:591
msgid "记录仅在成功推送后生成，请先触发一次推送并检查日志。"
msgstr "Records are created only after a successful push; trigger one and check logs."

